2026-05-14T06:51:35.5148271Z 22    <!--
2026-05-14T06:51:35.5148786Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-14T06:51:35.5150219Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-14T06:51:35.5150889Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
